OL,3,CNew cancer centre given the go ahead
OL,5,FDr George Findlay, Chief Executive,
OL,6,FUniversity Hospitals Sussex NHS Trust
OL,7,Fsays, "Sadly, the demand for cancer
OL,8,Fcare is going up quite considerably
OL,9,Fand our current cancer centers are
OL,10,Freally quite small and outdated. So
OL,11,Fthis new cancer centre will give us
OL,12,Falmost seven times the footprint,
OL,13,Fthree times the clinical space, and a
OL,14,Fmuch better environment for our staff
OL,15,Fto continue to deliver great care for
OL,16,Fpatients."
OL,18,FPatients can expect to see improved
OL,19,Ffacilities including:
